Uses of Package
com.i2group.apollo.externaldata.loader

  • Packages that use com.i2group.apollo.externaldata.loader 
    Package Description
    com.i2group.apollo.externaldata.loader
    Contains classes and interfaces for creating and managing items from an external data source in the Analysis Repository.
  • Classes in com.i2group.apollo.externaldata.loader used by com.i2group.apollo.externaldata.loader 
    Class and Description
    IClientConnectionBuilder
    A method for creating an IClientFactory, which enables a bulk data loader to authenticate with and then connect to i2 Analyze web services.
    IDataLoader
    A mechanism for creating, updating, deleting, and purging Items in an i2 Analyze item store based on XML data from an external data source.
    ItemAndCards
    A container for information that represents a particular version of an Item and some of the Cards that it contains.
